locations.title: Tornado
locations.description:
Roams throughout the area.  Causes you to take heavy damage when in close proximity.  
- Climb up onto the shipping containers and make your way west, jumping and climbing as necessary, until you reach the [top of the crane boom](https://mapgenie.io/stalker-2-heart-of-chornobyl/maps/the-zone?locationIds=415941).  
- From here, allow the tornado to pass into you, popping a medkit immediately before as not to die  
- If done right, you'll find yourself in the eye of the tornado near the floating [Weird Bolt](https://mapgenie.io/stalker-2-heart-of-chornobyl/maps/the-zone?locationIds=415268)

locations.title: Mist
locations.description:
Anomaly exists in 4 states with bloodsuckers in each.  You must navigate from one state to another, by attempting to leave through the mist, only to find yourself at the house again:
- Repeat this step until the basement is accessible.  
- Inside the basement, retrieve the key, head up through the tunnel into the house and use the key to unlock the door.  
- Run through the mist once more to spawn boxes inside the house.  
- Jump up on the boxes to get inside the attic, then break the boxes and planks on the floor in the attic and drop into the room with the Weird Pot artifact.
